    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as a young woman living in the slums of an industrial complex.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The ruling caste of the complex takes people from each district of the slums for all sorts of experimentation. This is the heavy price paid by the people living around the complex.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During one of these raids, she and others revolted and refused to give themselves up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This led to their deaths and the purge of their district.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Although dead, a voice was heard. A dark entity made an offer: Life and vengeance for bloodshed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now she’s ready, and she has nothing to fear anymore …</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Her only goal: <strong>Make them bleed</strong></p>",
